{"data":[{"date":"09:18 04/08","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Palestine n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/nguoi-palestine-noi-gi-khi-thua-nguoc-u23-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p to l\u1edbn v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap anh tr\u1edf n\u00ean t\u1ef1 tin h\u01a1n trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo.</h2><h2>C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau m\u00e0n l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine?</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau m\u00e0n l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau m\u00e0n l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/4/38230725_10209976210556579_816878594738356224_n_ntub-2218.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng in d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y \u1edf c\u1ea3 hai pha l\u00e0m b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y \u1edf c\u1ea3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0. \u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean anh chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng v\u1eeba t\u1ea7m \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng Anh \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u1ed1ng ch\u1ebf r\u1ed3i tung ra c\u00fa s\u00fat ch\u00e2n tr\u00e1i hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c kh\u00f4ng cho th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3, v\u1eabn l\u00e0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi pha tho\u00e1t xu\u1ed1ng r\u1ea5t nhanh t\u1eeb \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ea5m b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Quang H\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e3 tung ch\u00e2n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c bu\u1ed9c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n U23 Palestine ph\u1ea3i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi khen t\u1eeb gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap anh tr\u1edf n\u00ean kh\u00e1 t\u1ef1 tin.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u00e2m s\u1ef1: \u201cH\u00f4m nay c\u1ea3m x\u00fac c\u1ee7a em r\u1ea5t l\u00e0 vui v\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0y gi\u00fap cho em gi\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa nhi\u1ec1u \u00e1p l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 tinh th\u1ea7n t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 tin s\u1ebd th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o ng\u00e0y mai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra. Sau nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i.</p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/3/Highlight-Viet-Nam-vs-Palestine-.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguoi-palestine-noi-gi-khi-thua-nguoc-u23-viet-nam-168-193688.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/nguoi-palestine-noi-gi-khi-thua-nguoc-u23-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguoi-palestine-noi-gi-khi-thua-nguoc-u23-viet-nam-168-193688.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Palestine n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV \u0110T U23 Palestine cho r\u1eb1ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1edd s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/thang-palestine-hlv-park-hang-seo-van-so-lo-bai-292-193667.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/thang-palestin-hlv-park-hang-seo-van-so-lo-bai.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/thang-palestine-hlv-park-hang-seo-van-so-lo-bai-292-193667.html\">Th\u1eafng Palestine, HLV Park Hang Seo v\u1eabn s\u1ee3 l\u1ed9 b\u00e0i</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Park Hang Seo chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng U23 Palestine v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/toa-sang-truoc-palestine-cong-phuong-duoc-ca-ngoi-het-loi-168-193668.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/toa-sang-truoc-palestine-cong-phuong-duoc-ca-ngoi-het-loi.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/toa-sang-truoc-palestine-cong-phuong-duoc-ca-ngoi-het-loi-168-193668.html\">T\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ca ng\u1ee3i h\u1ebft l\u1eddi</span><br>\r\nThi \u0111\u1ea5u xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u1edbi 2 l\u1ea7n g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh ca ng\u1ee3i v\u00ec \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1982","checkdouble":"193688"},{"date":"09:22 04/08","title":"Barca tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 b\u00e1n Vidal ngay h\u00e8 n\u00e0y","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/barca-tuyen-bo-ban-vidal-ngay-he-nay.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Aleix Vidal \u0111\u00e3 r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi tr\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 c\u1ee7a Barca \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00e0 chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Sevilla.</h2><h2>Barca chia tay Vidal\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca b\u00e1n Vidal cho Sevilla ngay h\u00e8 n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Barca b\u00e1n Vidal cho Sevilla ngay h\u00e8 n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/barca-tuyen-bo-ban-vidal-ngay-he-nay.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Barca b\u00e1n Vidal cho Sevilla v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 ch\u1ec9 9 tri\u1ec7u euro</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh Aleix Vidal \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Sevilla m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 9 tri\u1ec7u euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nVidal \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn thua 2-4 c\u1ee7a Barca tr\u01b0\u1edbc Roma t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i ICC. Nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean t\u1ea1i Camp Nou. Anh ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 51 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n trong 3 n\u0103m qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Barca \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng Vidal \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng cho Los Blaugrana.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cAleix Vidal \u0111ang tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Barcelona ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 cho ph\u00e9p c\u1eadu \u1ea5y quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Vidal tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Sevilla</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i d\u00e0nh ch\u1ec9 1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Sevilla tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Barca. Nh\u01b0ng anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t mi\u1ebfng gh\u00e9p quan tr\u1ecdng gi\u00fap Sevilla gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch UEFA Super Cup v\u00e0 Europa League n\u0103m \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Barca, Vidal gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 danh hi\u1ec7u La Liga v\u00e0 3 C\u00fap nh\u00e0 Vua. Tuy v\u1eady, anh ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Aleix Vidal tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Ramon Sanchez Pizjuan \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u v\u1ee5 l\u00e0m \u0103n th\u1ee9 hai c\u1ee7a Barca v\u00e0 Sevilla h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, trung v\u1ec7 Clement Lenglet \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Barca v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35.9 tri\u1ec7u euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0i gi\u1edd, Barca c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Arturo Vidal t\u1eeb Bayern Munich. G\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 x\u1ee9 Catalonia c\u0169ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Malcom t\u1eeb Bordeaux v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea9y nhanh h\u01a1n n\u1eefa qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0a Arthur t\u1eeb Gremio t\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Barca:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-chinh-thuc-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-sao-khung-bayern-munich-180-193675.html\">Barca CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng sao kh\u1ee7ng Bayern Munich</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-co-co-hoi-so-huu-bom-tan-cua-barca-172-192623.html\">Arsenal c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i s\u1edf h\u1eefu bom t\u1ea5n c\u1ee7a Barca</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1981","checkdouble":"193689"},{"date":"09:45 04/08","title":"Morata: \"Chelsea may m\u1eafn v\u00ec chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Jorginho\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/morata-chelsea-may-man-vi-chieu-mo-duoc-jorginho.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Alvaro Morata khen Jorginho v\u00e0 cho r\u1eb1ng Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.</h2><h2>Morata khen ng\u1ee3i Jorginho</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jorginho \u0111\u00e3 gia nh\u1eadp s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc d\u00f9 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng li\u00ean h\u1ec7 m\u1eadt thi\u1ebft v\u1edbi Man City tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3. S\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a HLV Maurizio Sarri l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i cho s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Morata \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng cho r\u1eb1ng Jorginho s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Morata khen Jorginho tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap v\u1edbi Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Morata khen Jorginho tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap v\u1edbi Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/4/morata-chelsea-may-man-vi-chieu-mo-duoc-jorginho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Morata khen Jorginho tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap v\u1edbi Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 may m\u1eafn. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u1ed1t b\u1edfi v\u00ec Jorginho l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u00e0ng trai tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 Man City c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. S\u1ebd th\u1eadt t\u1ec7 n\u1ebfu Man City c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1eadu \u1ea5y thay v\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cJorginho l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi Chelsea l\u00fac n\u00e0y. B\u1edfi v\u00ec khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u1eafm gi\u1eef ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a cho m\u1ecdi \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cJorginho v\u00e0 Cesc Fabregas khi c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng l\u00e0 hai ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p nh\u01b0 h\u1ecd khi c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng. V\u00e0 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i th\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Morata ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean v\u1ec1 Hudson-Odoi</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u0169ng b\u1ecb \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh b\u1edfi sao tr\u1ebb Callum Hudson-Odoi. Nhi\u1ec1u chuy\u00ean gia c\u00f2n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tu\u1ed5i teen n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Chelsea \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o nh\u01b0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Ethan Ampadu v\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, khi b\u1ea1n theo d\u00f5i h\u1ecd thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00ec b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 hay 26 tu\u1ed5i. Nh\u01b0ng th\u1eadt ra h\u1ecd m\u1edbi 17. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cHudson-Odoi r\u1ea5t may m\u1eafn khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi t\u1eeb Hazard, Willian v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o kh\u00e1c trong \u0111\u1ed9i. H\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea7y t\u1ed1t. N\u1ebfu c\u1eadu \u1ea5y nghe l\u1eddi v\u00e0 theo d\u00f5i Willian, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Chelsea:<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-sarri-tiet-lo-so-tan-binh-con-lai-cap-ben-chelsea-o-he-2018-172-193673.html\">HLV Sarri ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 s\u1ed1 t\u00e2n binh c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea \u1edf H\u00e8 2018?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/courtois-se-roi-chelsea-cap-ben-real-o-he-2018-172-193672.html\">Courtois s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Chelsea c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Real \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1980","checkdouble":"193690"},{"date":"09:33 04/08","title":"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau m\u00e0n l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/cong-phuong-noi-gi-sau-man-len-dong-truoc-palestine.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p to l\u1edbn v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap anh tr\u1edf n\u00ean t\u1ef1 tin h\u01a1n trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo.</h2><h2>C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau m\u00e0n l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine?</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau m\u00e0n l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau m\u00e0n l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/4/38230725_10209976210556579_816878594738356224_n_ntub-2218.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng in d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y \u1edf c\u1ea3 hai pha l\u00e0m b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y \u1edf c\u1ea3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0. \u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean anh chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng v\u1eeba t\u1ea7m \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng Anh \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u1ed1ng ch\u1ebf r\u1ed3i tung ra c\u00fa s\u00fat ch\u00e2n tr\u00e1i hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c kh\u00f4ng cho th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3, v\u1eabn l\u00e0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi pha tho\u00e1t xu\u1ed1ng r\u1ea5t nhanh t\u1eeb \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ea5m b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Quang H\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e3 tung ch\u00e2n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c bu\u1ed9c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n U23 Palestine ph\u1ea3i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi khen t\u1eeb gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap anh tr\u1edf n\u00ean kh\u00e1 t\u1ef1 tin.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u00e2m s\u1ef1: \u201cH\u00f4m nay c\u1ea3m x\u00fac c\u1ee7a em r\u1ea5t l\u00e0 vui v\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0y gi\u00fap cho em gi\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa nhi\u1ec1u \u00e1p l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 tinh th\u1ea7n t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 tin s\u1ebd th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o ng\u00e0y mai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra. Sau nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i.</p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/3/Highlight-Viet-Nam-vs-Palestine-.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguoi-palestine-noi-gi-khi-thua-nguoc-u23-viet-nam-168-193688.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/nguoi-palestine-noi-gi-khi-thua-nguoc-u23-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguoi-palestine-noi-gi-khi-thua-nguoc-u23-viet-nam-168-193688.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Palestine n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV \u0110T U23 Palestine cho r\u1eb1ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1edd s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/thang-palestine-hlv-park-hang-seo-van-so-lo-bai-292-193667.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/thang-palestin-hlv-park-hang-seo-van-so-lo-bai.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/thang-palestine-hlv-park-hang-seo-van-so-lo-bai-292-193667.html\">Th\u1eafng Palestine, HLV Park Hang Seo v\u1eabn s\u1ee3 l\u1ed9 b\u00e0i</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Park Hang Seo chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng U23 Palestine v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/toa-sang-truoc-palestine-cong-phuong-duoc-ca-ngoi-het-loi-168-193668.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/toa-sang-truoc-palestine-cong-phuong-duoc-ca-ngoi-het-loi.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/toa-sang-truoc-palestine-cong-phuong-duoc-ca-ngoi-het-loi-168-193668.html\">T\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ca ng\u1ee3i h\u1ebft l\u1eddi</span><br>\r\nThi \u0111\u1ea5u xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u1edbi 2 l\u1ea7n g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh ca ng\u1ee3i v\u00ec \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1979","checkdouble":"193691"},{"date":"09:44 04/08","title":"Th\u1eafng Palestine, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/thang-palestine-u23-viet-nam-duoc-thuong-lon.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Palestine, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn th\u01b0\u1edfng n\u00f3ng t\u1eeb VFF.</h2><h2>U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Palestine</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 t\u1ecf ra y\u1ebfu th\u1ebf h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u1edf th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh, th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c song b\u00f9 l\u1ea1i l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u0103n \u00fd gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng T\u00e2y \u00c1 Palestine.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1eafng Palestine, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1eafng Palestine, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/video-tong-hop-u23-viet-nam-21-u23-palestine-giai-u23-quoc-te-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine. \u1ea2nh: Zing.vn</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ebft th\u00fac 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u, chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam sau hai pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a c\u1eb7p ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Anh \u0110\u1ee9c \u2013 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, trong khi ph\u00eda Palestine ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 b\u00e0n sau pha b\u1eadt cao \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u tung l\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n V\u0103n L\u00e2m c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Oday Dabbagh \u1edf ph\u00fat 29.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngay sau khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y k\u1ebft th\u00fac, Th\u1ee9 tr\u01b0\u1edfng B\u1ed9 VH, TT&DL L\u00ea Kh\u00e1nh H\u1ea3i c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c quan ch\u1ee9c VFF \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ed1ng s\u00e2n ch\u00fac m\u1eebng v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1edfng n\u00f3ng cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thay m\u1eb7t VFF, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch VFF L\u00ea H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ed1ng s\u00e2n ch\u00fac m\u1eebng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo v\u00e0 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u1edfng n\u00f3ng 400 tri\u1ec7u cho to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00e1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd, b\u1edfi U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng quan tr\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh th\u00eam chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Oman, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uzbekistan. N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111o\u1ea1t ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cong-phuong-noi-gi-sau-man-len-dong-truoc-palestine-168-193691.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/cong-phuong-noi-gi-sau-man-len-dong-truoc-palestine.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cong-phuong-noi-gi-sau-man-len-dong-truoc-palestine-168-193691.html\">C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau m\u00e0n l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine?</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p to l\u1edbn v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap anh tr\u1edf n\u00ean t\u1ef1 tin h\u01a1n trong nh\u1eefng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguoi-palestine-noi-gi-khi-thua-nguoc-u23-viet-nam-168-193688.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/nguoi-palestine-noi-gi-khi-thua-nguoc-u23-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguoi-palestine-noi-gi-khi-thua-nguoc-u23-viet-nam-168-193688.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Palestine n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV \u0110T U23 Palestine cho r\u1eb1ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1edd s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Highlight Viet Nam vs Palestine</strong><span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/3/Highlight-Viet-Nam-vs-Palestine-.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1978","checkdouble":"193692"},{"date":"10:36 04/08","title":"C\u1ef1u HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u1ebft l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/cuu-hlv-truong-dt-viet-nam-het-loi-khen-ngoi-ban-thang-cua-cong-phuong.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine, c\u1ef1u HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110TQG \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n S\u1ef9 Hi\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen cho phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</h2><h2>C\u1ef1u HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u1ebft l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf U23 c\u00fap Vinaphone 2018, \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung c\u1ee7a 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ngo\u00e0i 23 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Trung \u0110\u00f4ng Palestine.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ec3 cho \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc trong hi\u1ec7p 1 nh\u01b0ng b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 nh\u1edd c\u00e1c pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Anh \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u1ef1u HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u1ebft l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u1ef1u HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u1ebft l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/toa-sang-truoc-palestine-cong-phuong-duoc-ca-ngoi-het-loi.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Palestine</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp theo d\u00f5i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eebng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n S\u1ef9 Hi\u1ec3n cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;D\u00f9 \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ed5 \u00edch v\u1ec1 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tinh th\u1ea7n v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 2-1, t\u00f4i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu nghi\u00eam t\u00fac c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. T\u00f4i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p nhu\u1ea7n nhuy\u1ec5n. T\u00f4i cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, d\u00f9 h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi t\u1eadp trung \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 tu\u1ea7n nh\u01b0ng th\u1ebf l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t hoan ngh\u00eanh.&quot;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng S\u1ef9 Hi\u1ec3n c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n. V\u1edbi th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c b\u1ec1n b\u1ec9 c\u00f9ng n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111i b\u00f3ng l\u1eaft l\u00e9o, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt l\u1ea7n l\u00e0m kh\u1ed5 s\u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Palestine.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb c\u1ef1u thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110TQG n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a HAGL: &ldquo;H\u00f4m nay V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft, Quang H\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5.&nbsp;C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00f4m nay \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 tung \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho Anh \u0110\u1ee9c. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 hai r\u1ea5t quy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, chuy\u00ean gia n\u00e0y c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u00fd ki\u1ebfn \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p cho h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn sau:&nbsp;&quot;Trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 to cao b\u00ean ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u00fang ta ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng l\u00e0m sao \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng cho \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ea1t v\u00e0o t\u1eeb hai c\u00e1nh v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u01a1n, n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n b\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00ean m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc n\u1eefa th\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n thua&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o 19h30 ng\u00e0y 5/8 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c v\u1edbi U23 Oman, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa U23 Palestine s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi U23 Uzbekistan v\u00e0o l\u00fac 16h./.<br>\r\n<strong>Highlight Viet Nam vs Palestine<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/3/Highlight-Viet-Nam-vs-Palestine-.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thang-palestine-u23-viet-nam-duoc-thuong-lon-168-193692.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/thang-palestine-u23-viet-nam-duoc-thuong-lon.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thang-palestine-u23-viet-nam-duoc-thuong-lon-168-193692.html\">Th\u1eafng Palestine, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Palestine, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn th\u01b0\u1edfng n\u00f3ng t\u1eeb VFF.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cong-phuong-noi-gi-sau-man-len-dong-truoc-palestine-168-193691.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/cong-phuong-noi-gi-sau-man-len-dong-truoc-palestine.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cong-phuong-noi-gi-sau-man-len-dong-truoc-palestine-168-193691.html\">C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau m\u00e0n l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine?</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p to l\u1edbn v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap anh tr\u1edf n\u00ean t\u1ef1 tin h\u01a1n trong nh\u1eefng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguoi-palestine-noi-gi-khi-thua-nguoc-u23-viet-nam-168-193688.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/nguoi-palestine-noi-gi-khi-thua-nguoc-u23-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguoi-palestine-noi-gi-khi-thua-nguoc-u23-viet-nam-168-193688.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Palestine n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV \u0110T U23 Palestine cho r\u1eb1ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1edd s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1977","checkdouble":"193694"},{"date":"10:50 04/08","title":"B\u1ecb c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, HLV Uzbekistan g\u1eedi l\u1eddi th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c t\u1edbi U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/bi-cam-hoa-ngay-ra-quan-hlv-uzbekistan-gui-loi-thach-thuc-toi-u23-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a kh\u00f4ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Oman,  HLV \u0111\u1ed9i U23 Uzbekistan \u0111\u00e3 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</h2><h2>HLV Uzbekistan g\u1eedi l\u1eddi th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c t\u1edbi U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">U23 Uzbekistan g\u1eb7p Oman l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u khai m\u00e0n gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf U23 c\u00fap Vinaphone n\u0103m nay. Tuy nhi\u00ean tr\u00e1i v\u1edbi k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y di\u1ec5n ra v\u1edbi ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n ch\u1ec9 \u1edf m\u1ee9c trung b\u00ecnh.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">U23 Uzbekistan \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u1eeba v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m nay v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 0-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Oman. Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, HLV Khaydarov c\u1ee7a Olympic Uzbekistan \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed5 l\u1ed7i cho y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\" B\u1ecb c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a, HLV Uzbekistan g\u1eedi l\u1eddi th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c t\u1edbi U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\" B\u1ecb c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a, HLV Uzbekistan g\u1eedi l\u1eddi th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c t\u1edbi U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/4/u23-uzbekistan-01-2013.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Uzbekistan tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng Khaydarov n\u00f3i: \u201cH\u00f4m nay l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, kh\u00ed h\u1eadu n\u00f3ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m cao n\u00ean c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01b0a k\u1ecbp th\u00edch nghi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 2-3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i \u0111\u00fang phong \u0111\u1ed9, \u00edt c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o ra trong hi\u1ec7p 1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Uzbekistan c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i trong hi\u1ec7p 2 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. N\u00f3i t\u00f3m l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t.\"\u00a0\u00a0 <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, HLV Khaydarov ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c Olympic Uzbekistan gi\u1ea5u b\u00e0i, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i: \"Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea5u b\u00e0i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Olympic Uzbekistan l\u00e0 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t, th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 mong mu\u1ed1n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ea1nh, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft. Nh\u01b0ng Uzbekistan s\u1ebd th\u1eafng \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.\"<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede ph\u00eda b\u00ean kia, HLV Oman c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m quen v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n kh\u00ed h\u1eadu n\u00f3ng \u1ea9m, nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9 cao t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i. Tuy nhi\u00ean nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n n\u00e0y c\u0169ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o 19h30 ng\u00e0y 5/8 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0110T U23 Oman s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c v\u1edbi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa U23 Palestine s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi U23 Uzbekistan v\u00e0o l\u00fac 16h./.</p>\r\n<h3>Highlight Viet Nam vs Palestine<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span></h3>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/3/Highlight-Viet-Nam-vs-Palestine-.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cuu-hlv-truong-dt-viet-nam-het-loi-khen-ngoi-ban-thang-cua-cong-phuong-168-193694.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/cuu-hlv-truong-dt-viet-nam-het-loi-khen-ngoi-ban-thang-cua-cong-phuong.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cuu-hlv-truong-dt-viet-nam-het-loi-khen-ngoi-ban-thang-cua-cong-phuong-168-193694.html\">C\u1ef1u HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u1ebft l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine, c\u1ef1u HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110TQG \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n S\u1ef9 Hi\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen cho phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thang-palestine-u23-viet-nam-duoc-thuong-lon-168-193692.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/thang-palestine-u23-viet-nam-duoc-thuong-lon.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thang-palestine-u23-viet-nam-duoc-thuong-lon-168-193692.html\">Th\u1eafng Palestine, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Palestine, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn th\u01b0\u1edfng n\u00f3ng t\u1eeb VFF.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguoi-palestine-noi-gi-khi-thua-nguoc-u23-viet-nam-168-193688.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/nguoi-palestine-noi-gi-khi-thua-nguoc-u23-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguoi-palestine-noi-gi-khi-thua-nguoc-u23-viet-nam-168-193688.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Palestine n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV \u0110T U23 Palestine cho r\u1eb1ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1edd s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";=\"\" color:#111111\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1976","checkdouble":"193695"},{"date":"11:18 04/08","title":"U23 Th\u00e1i Lan thua \u0111au \u0111\u1ed9i U19 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/4/u23-thai-lan-thua-dau-doi-u19-han-quoc-truoc-them-asiad.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i \u0111ang c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t cho ASIAD khi ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn thua li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Myanmar.</h2><h2>U23 Th\u00e1i Lan thua \u0111au \u0111\u1ed9i U19 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eadn l\u1eddi tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf Alpine Cup 2018 t\u1ea1i Myanmar, U23 Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u00e3 mang theo \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n cho b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 x\u1ee9 ch\u00f9a V\u00e0ng tranh t\u00e0i t\u1ea1i ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Myanmar, nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch SEA Games 2017 \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. Sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 2-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Bahrain \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, \u2018nh\u1eefng ch\u00fa voi Th\u00e1i\u2019 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tr\u1eafng tay trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 U19 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"U23 Th\u00e1i Lan thua \u0111au \u0111\u1ed9i U19 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"U23 Th\u00e1i Lan thua \u0111au \u0111\u1ed9i U19 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/4/thailand-korea_k4q4r6zn2eei1dkoxiu2bh3nt.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>U23 Th\u00e1i Lan (xanh) ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 thua k\u00e9m \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1edbi 3,4 tu\u1ed5i tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u \u00c1, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n tr\u1ebb H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c nhanh ch\u00f3ng b\u1eaft nh\u1ecbp v\u00e0 b\u00e0y ra th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1edbi v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Kim chi c\u0169ng l\u00e0 h\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea5t y\u1ebfu. Ngay trong hi\u1ec7p 1, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n U23 Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i hai l\u1ea7n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng khi Lim Jae-huyk v\u00e0 Um Won-sang t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf c\u00e1c ph\u00fat 28 v\u00e0 44.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u00e0m v\u1ed1n trong hi\u1ec7p 1, b\u01b0\u1edbc sang hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo, U19 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 v\u1ebb ch\u1ee7 quan. V\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 2-2 trong hai ph\u00fat t\u1eeb\u00a049 \u0111\u1ebfn 51. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, b\u1eb1ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, U19 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1eabn gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c 4-2.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn Th\u00e1i Lan b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y xu\u1ed1ng b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng khi ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 n\u00e0o. Quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n, nh\u1eefng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a U23 Th\u00e1i Lan khi m\u00e0 ASIAD \u0111ang t\u1edbi r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u0103m nay, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i n\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng B c\u0169ng \u0110KV\u0110 U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 Uzbekistan, \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ea1ng 3 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 Qatar c\u00f9ng U23 Bangladesh. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9, vi\u1ec7c Th\u00e1i Lan b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i s\u1edbm ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 x\u1ea3y ra.\u00a0<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bi-cam-hoa-ngay-ra-quan-hlv-uzbekistan-gui-loi-thach-thuc-toi-u23-viet-nam-168-193695.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/bi-cam-hoa-ngay-ra-quan-hlv-uzbekistan-gui-loi-thach-thuc-toi-u23-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bi-cam-hoa-ngay-ra-quan-hlv-uzbekistan-gui-loi-thach-thuc-toi-u23-viet-nam-168-193695.html\">B\u1ecb c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, HLV Uzbekistan g\u1eedi l\u1eddi th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c t\u1edbi U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a kh\u00f4ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Oman,  HLV \u0111\u1ed9i U23 Uzbekistan \u0111\u00e3 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cuu-hlv-truong-dt-viet-nam-het-loi-khen-ngoi-ban-thang-cua-cong-phuong-168-193694.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/cuu-hlv-truong-dt-viet-nam-het-loi-khen-ngoi-ban-thang-cua-cong-phuong.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cuu-hlv-truong-dt-viet-nam-het-loi-khen-ngoi-ban-thang-cua-cong-phuong-168-193694.html\">C\u1ef1u HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u1ebft l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine, c\u1ef1u HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110TQG \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n S\u1ef9 Hi\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen cho phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguoi-palestine-noi-gi-khi-thua-nguoc-u23-viet-nam-168-193688.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/nguoi-palestine-noi-gi-khi-thua-nguoc-u23-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguoi-palestine-noi-gi-khi-thua-nguoc-u23-viet-nam-168-193688.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Palestine n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV \u0110T U23 Palestine cho r\u1eb1ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1edd s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1975","checkdouble":"193696"},{"date":"07:05 04/08","title":"Morata quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ed1c ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/morata-quyet-dinh-soc-ngay-truoc-them-mua-giai-moi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Inter Milan mu\u1ed1n mua Matteo Darmian, theo Gianluca Di Marzio ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Darmian mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi M.U</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Matteo Darmian kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o M.U. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1989 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, Mourinho kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Napoli, Inter Milan mu\u1ed1n mua Matteo Darmian h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"V\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Napoli, Inter Milan mu\u1ed1n mua Matteo Darmian h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/them-mot-doi-bong-hoi-mua-hau-ve-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Darmian mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1eeb khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn M.U, Darmian ch\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i sao kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. D\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Mourinho c\u1ef1u sao Torino b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ra kh\u1ecfi k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng: \u201c\u0110\u00fang l\u00e0 Darmian \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1eb7p t\u00f4i \u0111\u00f2i ra \u0111i, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, t\u00f4i khuy\u00ean c\u1eadu \u1ea5y n\u00ean ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, n\u1ebfu c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ra \u0111i t\u00f4i s\u1ebd t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Valencia d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi kh\u1edfi tranh l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Mourinho bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch gi\u1eef Darmian \u1edf l\u1ea1i, song v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh Dalot n\u1ebfu h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 ra \u0111i \u00f4ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng gi\u1eef.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Inter Milan h\u1ecfi mua Darmian</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Inter Milan mu\u1ed1n mua Matteo Darmian, theo Gianluca Di Marzio ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Matteo Darmian\" title=\"Matteo Darmian\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/30/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-307-lo-dien-ben-do-bat-ngo-cua-hau-ve-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Inter Milan h\u1ecfi mua Matteo Darmian</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Inter l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn Darmian \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, song th\u1ea5t th\u1ebf v\u1edbi Juventus l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd r\u00fat lui trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn\u00a0\u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng m\u1eb7n m\u00e0 v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a M.U, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan \u0111\u00e3 quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c M.U b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i, ph\u00eda Inter Milan ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. H\u1ecd tin r\u1eb1ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y s\u1ebd thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Inter Milan th\u00ec <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/dai-gia-italia-chua-buong-tha-matteo-darmian-172-192507.html\" target=\"_blank\">Napoli c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Darmian</span>. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n San Paolo \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecfi m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, sau \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd chuy\u1ec3n sang h\u1ecfi mua. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Darmian quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ra \u0111i, cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia gi\u1eefa Inter v\u00e0 Napoli \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n r\u1ea5t kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1974","checkdouble":"193676"},{"date":"07:57 04/08","title":"Real \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 mua th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o hay kh\u00f4ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/real-dua-ra-quyet-dinh-co-mua-them-tien-dao-hay-khong.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng mua th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd trao nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i h\u01a1n cho Borja Mayoral.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat t\u1ed1t</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Real Madrid \u0111\u00e1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Morata cho Chelsea v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng mua th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng mua th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/Chuyen-nhuong-Real-Madrid-2018-quyet-dinh-khong-mua-them-tien-dao-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Lopetegui quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng mua th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, khi m\u00e0 Ronaldo \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a c\u00f2n Benzema g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, Los Blancos kh\u00f4ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Th\u1ea5t th\u1ebf \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Barca \u1edf La Liga khi\u1ebfn K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra cu\u1ed9c l\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed5 \u1edf n\u1eeda sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, Real \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 CR7, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ghi kho\u1ea3ng 50 b\u00e0n/m\u00f9a, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u1ee7a Real.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n cho r\u1eb1ng Real bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i mua ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng b\u1ed5 sung m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u0103n b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd s\u1ebd b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/them-mot-tien-dao-khung-lot-vao-tam-ngam-cua-real-madrid-180-191967.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real quan t\u00e2m Cavani c\u1ee7a PSG</span>, Harry Kane v\u00e0 Robert Lewandowski c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng mua th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng mua th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o, HLV Lopetegui kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, m\u00f9a t\u1edbi Real v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Benzema ghi ban vao luoi M.U\" title=\"Benzema ghi ban vao luoi M.U\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/Benzema-ghi-ban-vao-luoi-M.U.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Benzema\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng v\u1edbi Cavani, Harry Kane v\u00e0 Robert Lewandowski, h\u1ecd \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i v\u00e0o Karim Benzema, ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 31 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Lopetegui d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n cho ch\u00e2n s\u00fat tr\u1ebb Borja Mayoral, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha tin t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Benzema chia s\u1ebb g\u00e1nh n\u1eb7ng ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Borja Mayoral ra s\u00e2n 14 l\u1ea7n \u1edf La Liga, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. \u00d4ng Lopetegui tin r\u1eb1ng s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Ronaldo s\u1ebd gi\u00fap ng\u00f4i sao 21 tu\u1ed5i tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1973","checkdouble":"193677"},{"date":"08:12 04/08","title":"Man City ch\u1ec9 mua th\u00eam c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1ebfu...","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/16/man-city-chi-mua-them-cau-thu-neu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Pep Guardiola n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Man City 2018, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Man xanh ch\u1ec9 mua th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m n\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man City mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/man-city-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-mahrez-172-190895.html\" target=\"_blank\">Man City mua\u00a0 Riyad Mahrez t\u1eeb Leicester </span>v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Man xanh t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Pep v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Pep Guardiola n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Man City 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Pep Guardiola n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Man City 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/HLV-Pep-Guardiola-noi-ve-chuyen-nhuong-Man-City-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Man City nh\u1eafm Isco \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Mirror, HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m, ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebd thay th\u1ebf l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho David Silva, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 32 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng qu\u00e1 t\u1ed1t.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMan City quan t\u00e2m Jorginho c\u1ee7a Napoli, song h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Jorginho v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 57 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111\u00e3 t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi HLV Sarri \u1edf Stamford Bridge thay v\u00ec t\u1edbi Etihad.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Jorginho bu\u1ed9c Man City ph\u1ea3i chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c, hi\u1ec7n h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 Toni Kroos, Isco hay Mateo Kovacic c\u1ee7a Real, Pjanic c\u1ee7a Juventus hay Ramsey c\u1ee7a Arsenal.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Pep n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c mua th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Pep Guardiola n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Man City 2018, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Man xanh ch\u1ec9 mua th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m n\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pep Guardiola\" title=\"Pep Guardiola\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/Chi-80-trieu-euro,-Man-City-muon-mua-Marco-Verratti-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pep Guardiola n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c mua th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cN\u1ebfu Man City mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m, ngo\u00e0i t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 cho t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. T\u00e2n binh \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa m\u00e0 c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. B\u00e2y gi\u1edd ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n t\u1eadp trung nghi\u00eam tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1edfi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi s\u1eafp kh\u1edfi tranh. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1972","checkdouble":"193678"},{"date":"08:25 04/08","title":"Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u1ecfi mua h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/them-mot-doi-bong-hoi-mua-hau-ve-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Inter Milan mu\u1ed1n mua Matteo Darmian, theo Gianluca Di Marzio ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Darmian mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi M.U</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Matteo Darmian kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o M.U. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1989 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, Mourinho kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Napoli, Inter Milan mu\u1ed1n mua Matteo Darmian h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"V\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Napoli, Inter Milan mu\u1ed1n mua Matteo Darmian h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/them-mot-doi-bong-hoi-mua-hau-ve-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Darmian mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1eeb khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn M.U, Darmian ch\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i sao kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. D\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Mourinho c\u1ef1u sao Torino b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ra kh\u1ecfi k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng: \u201c\u0110\u00fang l\u00e0 Darmian \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1eb7p t\u00f4i \u0111\u00f2i ra \u0111i, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, t\u00f4i khuy\u00ean c\u1eadu \u1ea5y n\u00ean ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, n\u1ebfu c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ra \u0111i t\u00f4i s\u1ebd t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Valencia d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi kh\u1edfi tranh l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Mourinho bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch gi\u1eef Darmian \u1edf l\u1ea1i, song v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh Dalot n\u1ebfu h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 ra \u0111i \u00f4ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng gi\u1eef.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Inter Milan h\u1ecfi mua Darmian</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Inter Milan mu\u1ed1n mua Matteo Darmian, theo Gianluca Di Marzio ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Matteo Darmian\" title=\"Matteo Darmian\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/30/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-307-lo-dien-ben-do-bat-ngo-cua-hau-ve-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Inter Milan h\u1ecfi mua Matteo Darmian</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Inter l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn Darmian \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, song th\u1ea5t th\u1ebf v\u1edbi Juventus l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd r\u00fat lui trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn\u00a0\u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng m\u1eb7n m\u00e0 v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a M.U, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan \u0111\u00e3 quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c M.U b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i, ph\u00eda Inter Milan ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. H\u1ecd tin r\u1eb1ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y s\u1ebd thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Inter Milan th\u00ec <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/dai-gia-italia-chua-buong-tha-matteo-darmian-172-192507.html\" target=\"_blank\">Napoli c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Darmian</span>. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n San Paolo \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecfi m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, sau \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd chuy\u1ec3n sang h\u1ecfi mua. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Darmian quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ra \u0111i, cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia gi\u1eefa Inter v\u00e0 Napoli \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n r\u1ea5t kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1971","checkdouble":"193679"},{"date":"07:11 04/08","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay (4/8/2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-482018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay 4/8 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt chi ti\u1ebft l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u00f4ng tin ng\u00e0y gi\u1edd c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 di\u1ec5n ra h\u00f4m nay v\u00e0 \u0111\u00eam/r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y mai.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay 4-8-2018 v\u00e0 r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng ng\